## Priority 1: Essential Foundation (Do First)
These are quick wins that will make everything else easier.

### 1. **Keep Chrome Open After Task** ⚡ [30 mins]
**Why first:** This is crucial for debugging and continuing work. Super easy to implement.
```python
# In your agent.py, use:
browser_session = BrowserSession(
    browser_profile=BrowserProfile(
        user_data_dir='C:/Users/drmcn/.config/browseruse/profiles/default',
        keep_alive=True  # Add this
    )
)
# Then after agent.run():
input('Press Enter to close browser...')
await browser_session.kill()
```

